    dc:title "A revision of dragon millipedes III: the new genus Gigaxytes gen. nov., with the description of three new species (Diplopoda, Polydesmida, Paradoxosomatidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5542446>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5542448>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5542452>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5542454> ;
