<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5542446>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Gigaxytes fusca Srisonchai, Enghoff & Panha gen. et sp. nov., Ƌ paratype. Watercolour by Photchana Kriatpraprai." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5542446/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5542448>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. General body characters of Gigaxytes gen. nov. (G. fusca Srisonchai, Enghoff & Panha gen. et sp. nov., Ƌ paratype) – SEM images. A–B. Anterior body part (arrowheads point to pleurosternal carinae). C. Collum. D. Body rings 9–10. E. Body rings 8–10. F. Telson. G. Posteriormost rings and telson. H. Body ring 10. I. Mouthparts, ventral view. J. Ƌ leg 13. K. Sternal lobe between Ƌ coxae 4. L, N. Tip of epiproct. M. Tip of tarsus and claw of leg 13." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5542448/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5542452>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. SEM images of right gonopod of Gigaxytes Srisonchai, Enghoff & Panha gen. nov. – Gigaxytes gigas (Golovatch & Enghoff, 1994) gen. et comb. nov., ³, specimen from Wat Tham Sue (Tiger Cave). A. Lateral view. B. Mesal view. C. Dorsal view. D. Ventral view. Colours: red = lamina medialis, yellow = solenomere, green = lamina lateralis, purple = seminal groove." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5542452/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5542454>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. A–C. Photographs of live Gigaxytes fusca Srisonchai, Enghoff & Panha gen. et sp. nov. A. Ƌ paratype, specimen from Phitsadarn Cave. B. Ƌ paratype, specimen from Phrayarhtan Cave (Buddha Cave). C. ♀ paratype, specimen from Phitsadarn Cave. D–E. Phoretic histiostomatid mites. F. Habitat." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5542454/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

